summary:
Born and raised in Italy. Studied in Japan, California and Italy, where I graduated from the prestigious Ca' Foscari University of Venice. Experience working in Australia, Portugal, Germany and Netherlands, gaining valuable cultural and industry experience in working with cross-cultural teams, including decision-making, team building and hiring. Now based in lovely Amsterdam, working as a Project Manager in HR, creating products for our employees.
Languages lover, currently learning my 8th language, with the ultimate goal of speaking fluently 10 languages. 

Speak to me in your language, and I will try to understand :)
